title: Pull request merge from GaelVaroquaux/nilearn:api_moves to nilearn/nilearn:master

text: @pgervais , @AlexandreAbraham : I am ready to be merged with this PR. After it's merged, I suggest that you rebase all your branch (all your rebases are belong to us!), because this PR has touched upon a lot of files, and will create conflicts.

OK, I am merging this branch, because I need it for other work that I am
doing in parallel. Too bad that I didn't get a review from @pgervais.
Post-merge reviews appreciated anyhow
